Package: tablr
Title: user-friendly and tidy R crosstabs
Version: 0.2.1.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Brice",
           family = "Nocenti",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "brice.nocenti@gmail.com")
Description: If R makes complex things simple, it can sometimes make simple things difficult. This is why tablr try to make it easy to deal with multiple crosstabs: to create, manipulate, color and export tabs and lists of tabs to Excel. All functions are tidyverse-propelled, render tibbles, and are pipe-friendly. In development.
